info.smart_tools.smartactors.utils.ioc.strategy

Class ArgMatchingGeneralStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • info.smart_tools.smartactors.utils.ioc.strategy.ArgMatchingGeneralStrategy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GeneralStrategy

    public abstract class ArgMatchingGeneralStrategy
extends Object
implements GeneralStrategy
    GeneralStrategy that calls getInstanceStrategy(StrategyKey) when target class and argument classes match classes defined on initialization. Note: for matching arguments is used Class.isAssignableFrom(Class) so this will work if instances of subclasses of expected argument classes are passed as arguments.
